### CN simulator

The CN simulator computes scores for competitors from the FFCO. It is just a simulation and there is no warranty about the accuracy of scores. You can use this function to check that data are ok for publication. Use the *OE CSV* checkbox in the export file dialog.

Check the correctness of archive ids to ensure ok results! Best way to do it is simply to use archive import or CSV import.

