## Autoexport

The *Autoexport* button, when on (pressed), repeatedly refreshes results or generates a result file called `lastresults` in the data folder with the interval specified (in seconds) in the textfield at the right.
The autoexport feature takes into account parameters specified when the button is pressed (selected courses or categories, export format, *Show NC*,...).
Stop then start again autoexport to take into account new parameters.
